Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.04,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,チャ～ンス
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.47,0:00:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He picks on the weak and sucks up to the strong. He's lazy and a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:33.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者にむち打ち　強者にへつらい
